CS RANGER: Elite Coalition scout and wilderness operator

The CS Ranger is an elite Coalition scout operating deep behind enemy
lines. Better trained than the standard Grunt, Rangers combine military
discipline with wilderness survival and advanced reconnaissance skills.

CS Rangers begin with a broad military and survival skill base and
choose from Espionage, Military, Physical, Pilot, Technical, and W.P.
categories.

STARTING PACKAGE
  Attribute requirements: IQ 8, PS 10, PE 10.
  Equipment: Light Coalition scout armor, energy pistol, sniper rifle,
    survival backpack, camouflage field uniform, and Coalition ID.

